13
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:53,940
Bye.

14
00:02:53,940 --> 00:02:55,020
You pretended?

15
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,370
You seem fine.

16
00:03:05,070 --> 00:03:06,160
Go now.

17
